        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"112680\">Johan Commelin</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/217875-Is-there-code-for-X.3F/topic/Zp.20is.20compact.3F/near/467727228\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>huh?! I'm sure it must be there</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Yes, that was my reaction too <span aria-label=\"surprise\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f62e\" role=\"img\" title=\"surprise\">:surprise:</span></p>",
