        "content": "<p>I am working on this, almost there. I think <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"741361\">@Jou Glasheen</span> has the precise result for Z_p while my PRs are converging to the general result about the conditions for a nonarchimedean field to be locally compact.</p>",
