    {
        "content": "<p>Finite residue field portion: <a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/pull/15424\">#15424</a><br>\nComplete iff unit ball complete: <a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/pull/15777\">#15777</a><br>\nIsPrincipalIdealRing iff not DenselyOrdered: <a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/tree/pechersky%2Fvaluation-integers-zm0\">branch#pechersky/valuation-integers-zm0</a></p>",
