        "content": "<blockquote>\n<p>My student Giulio Caflisch at ETH is working on getting Mahler's theorem itself into mathlib.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>PR <a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/pull/19340\">#19340</a> adds the key technical lemma for Mahler's theorem, which is that the iterated forward differences<code>Δ^[n] f 0</code> tend to 0 for all continuous functions <code>f</code> on <code>ℤ_[p]</code>.</p>",
